{"tid":1931651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太子站閉路電視片段只可用作民事訴訟，不能向公眾披露","createTime":"2020-03-18T09:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T10:15:27.000Z","uid":276323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1b976192c5b7feeb8a3de0551a6e99463408fec5","tid":1931651,"uid":276323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:23:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B93lGQkHLjH/?igshid=1wt0syv17x1jh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB93lGQkHLjH%2F%3Figshid%3D1wt0syv17x1jh&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=85cb9737\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB93lGQkHLjH%2F%3Figshid%3D1wt0syv17x1jh&h=b00e8203\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B93lGQkHLjH/?igshid=1wt0syv17x1jh</a>［保持獨立思考 切密跟車太貼］<br />\n法官今日再頒下判詞，接納梁耀霆的申請，下令港鐵於七日內向梁交出相關的閉路電視錄影片段。<br />\n<br />\n法官下令，港鐵須向梁耀霆交出太子站去年8月31日當晚10時40分至9月1日凌晨1時30分、以及荔枝角站9月1日凌晨1時25分至2時正的閉路電視錄影片段。 【案件編號：HCMP1441/19】<br />\n/<br />\n無錯 法官的確下令港鐵須交出831閉路電視<br />\n但對象只限教育大學學生會會長梁耀霆與其律師團隊<br />\n「暫時並不是向公眾披露」！！！<br />\n/<br />\n唔好以為咁樣算贏咗，根據Now新聞台嘅報道 港鐵已經將全部閉路電視交比警方<br />\n市民入稟就831衝突向警方索償　明年6月再訊<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374457&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374457%26refer%3DShare&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=879b9ca2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374457%26refer%3DShare&h=40a7d678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374457&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n而根據公開資料守則，市民有權要求政府公開現存於警方嘅全數片段。<br />\n但若資料披露對「公眾利益」造成損害，政府有權不披露資料。<br />\n<br />\n顯而言之，向公眾披露片段唔會對公眾利益造成損害。<br />\n同時，政府亦係港鐡最大股東，佢地如果係想公開片段可以有幾難操作？<br />\n<br />\n我地唔單止要受害人可以睇返當晚嘅片段，關乎公眾利益，我地要全部人都可以睇，我地要政府「向公眾公開」當晚片段。<br />\n<br />\n既然法治而死，我們便直接挑戰極權。<br />\n<br />\n#香港思流 <br />\n#太子站<br />\n#831閉路電視"},{"pid":"a9b4c04ef1c1aeb6856a8698aabb0e7806f22d41","tid":1931651,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:24:58.000Z","msg":"搵到當時咩事先<br />\n點算賬可以再思考"},{"pid":"01c612fde15869b0d95aace7fbfe562e7f965b51","tid":1931651,"uid":54415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:25:33.000Z","msg":"收得齊D片先再講"},{"pid":"5bd79ac2f590dcee7ae5cfaa2a2e8438974b85e3","tid":1931651,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2stC8YY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2stC8YY.jpg&h=9f623ce2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}